  "display_name": "Rabies epidemiology and control",
  "description": "This cluster of papers focuses on the epidemiology, transmission dynamics, control strategies, and host-pathogen interactions of the Rabies virus. It covers topics such as the role of bats as reservoir hosts, canine rabies burden estimation, human rabies neuropathogenesis, viral transneuronal tracing, vaccination campaigns, and the molecular virology of Rabies.",
